      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller diameter and volute topology with the subject CPB device. Operating points span the clinical CPB envelope (3–6 L/min, 3000–5000 RPM). Geometric deviations from the predicate device are within ±8% on key hydraulic dimensions, considered acceptable for MRL 2."
    },
